  is '商家优惠金额，单位:分(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.plat_discount_amount
  is '平台优惠金额，单位:分(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.mch_rate_type
  is '费率类型，1.按比列;2.按阶梯(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.mch_rate
  is '商户费率，百万单位存储(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.cost_rate
  is '通道费率，百万单位存储(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.mch_theory_procedure_fee
  is '商户理论手续费，单位:分(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.mch_real_procedure_fee
  is '商户实际手续费，单位:分(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.mch_discount_fee
  is '商户手续费减免金额，单位:分(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.debit_card_brokerage_limit
  is '商户封顶手续费，单位:分(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.calc_state
  is '手续费计算状态，0:初始,1.计算成功,2.计算失败(计费字段，后续拆分)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.api_provider
  is '接口提供方，数据来源：cms_sys_type，type_class = API_PROVIDER';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.acc_way_period
  is '结算周期';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.pay_center_id
  is '支付通道ID，对应通道表主键';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.quick_serial_no
  is '快捷支付流水号';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.acct_dt
  is '会计日，格式20240808';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_AMSS_PAY_ORDER.start_dt
  is '开始时间';
